Meet <b>AJ</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>This Lakeview resident has only lived in Millsberry since April 3, 2007! But in just over two months she has collected quite a few trophies and started fixing up her home at <a href='/home/?user=gingersnappea'>83391-B Pond Road</a>. She plans to build many more rooms and make it the perfect place to hang out this summer.<br><br>AJ has a great sense of humor and is always making people laugh. When she acts in school plays, she often plays a jokester. She is also a musician who loves modern rock, pop, and rap. Her strong opinions have made her one of Millsberry's most memorable citizens. She's not afraid to tell people how she feels!<br><br>At heart, AJ is an animal lover who would be happy to stay home with her pets all day. Lakeview is a great neighborhood for a girl with rambunctious furry friends. Stop by her home if you're in the area, and don't hesitate to send her a little housewarming gift. After all, she is one of Millsberry's newest arrivals.<br><br>Welcome to town, AJ, and thanks for being a good citizen. Congratulations on being named Citizen of the Week!</div>
